description: Adds an asset, such as a dashboard, analysis, or dataset into a folder.

parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The ID for the Amazon Web Services account that contains the folder.

parameters.name: MemberId
parameters.description: The ID of the asset that you want to add to the folder.

parameters.name: MemberType
parameters.description: The member type of the asset that you want to add to a folder.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.

nested_items.name: FolderMember
nested_items.description: Information about the member in the folder.

nested_items.name: MemberId
nested_items.description: The ID of an asset in the folder.

nested_items.name: MemberType
nested_items.description: The type of asset that it is.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.
